high_descs: Walk to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the egg in front of the paper towels.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the right.
Put the egg in the fridge on the top shelf next to the white mug, close the door, open the door, take the egg out, close the door.
Turn right and walk to the microwave straight ahead.
Open the microwave door, put the egg inside of the microwave, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To chill an egg and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to face the egg on the counter.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the egg in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and cross the room to face the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool an egg plus place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the counter with the potato on it
Pick up the potato from the counter
Turn around, walk to the fridge on the right
Open the fridge, place the potato inside. Close the fridge, let cool. Open the fridge and remove the potato
Turn to the right, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave and place the potato inside.
